NTF-Demo v2.0 Binary Test File
Corresponding to: cpu_examples/8bit_example.hdr

Instructions (hex):
00        ; nop
10        ; mov ax, ax
15        ; mov bx, bx
2A        ; add cx, imm_1
3F        ; sub dx, imm_5
50        ; inc ax
64        ; dec bx
78        ; xor cx, ax
80 10     ; jmp 0x10
90 00     ; push ax
A0 01     ; pop bx
00        ; nop

Note: This is NOT a valid binary file.
The actual binary must be created with:
  python -c "import sys; sys.stdout.buffer.write(bytes([0x00,0x10,0x15,0x2A,0x3F,0x50,0x64,0x78,0x80,0x10,0x90,0x00,0xA0,0x01,0x00]))" > tests/test_binary.bin
